##Four days after the Hubei Village official was killed in the line of duty, his son made a decision

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Wu Yi is a reporter for the paper

"He said that every day is like a war and he can't stop it. Now the task of prevention and control of the epidemic in the spring is quite heavy and he can't rest assured. "

On February 15, Huang told www.thepaper.cn  The Paper that his younger brother, Harvard, Secretary of the Party branch of Shuizhai village, Yandian town, Anlu city, Xiaogan City, Hubei Province, fell on the frontline of epidemic prevention and control more than 10 days ago, never to rise again.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Huang Hanming, secretary of the Party branch of Shuizhai village, Yandian town, Xiaogan City, Hubei Province. The official wechat account of Anlu's Communist Party propaganda department shows a picture of an Lu

On February 2,2020, Comrade Huang Hanming suffered from double pulmonary emphysema and heart failure due to overwork. He collapsed in the first line of prevention and control of the epidemic. He was only 57.

"Don't drop the ball in a critical period. " At about 9 a.m. on February 1, just one hour before he died in the line of duty, Huang Hanming was still making arrangements for deployment, in particular, people returning from Wuhan have to take the survey once a day in the morning and afternoon, and report the survey to the town office at 11:30 a.m. and 5 p.m.

This became Huang Hanming in"Water Village Village Village Affairs Group"the last work information that releases. On February 2, the Xiaogan Municipal Party Committee decided to Posthumously Award Comrade Huang Hanming the title of "Outstanding Communist Party member of the city" .

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
One hour before he died in the line of duty, Huang Hanming was still making arrangements. The official wechat account of Anlu's Communist Party propaganda department shows a picture of an Lu

Go door-to-door

Huang told The Paper that his younger brother, the fourth oldest, had worked for 30 years as the village's Communist Party secretary. Huang Hanming is a veteran, joined the army in 1979, returned to his hometown in 1984 after returning to the army, in 1990 began to serve as secretary of the Party branch of Shuizhai village.

This year, the new coronavirus is raging. Shuizhai village is located in the outskirts of Anlu city. There are 11 village groups with 486 families and 1,974 people. Among them, 92 people returned home from Wuhan to celebrate the Lunar New Year. Therefore, Shuizhai village was listed as Anlu epidemic prevention and control key village.

Since January 23, Huang has devoted himself to the front line of Epidemic Prevention and control, carrying out propaganda for epidemic prevention and control, registering and checking the situation of people returning home, going from house to house to measure the body temperature of villagers, and so on, and in the Haoqiao community into the village intersection of water check check check traffic personnel and vehicles.

Huang Fuming revealed that his brother Huang Hanming long-term suffering from Emphysema, have more than 10 years of history of asthma, recent physical discomfort. But he still adhere to the prevention and control line, go door to door investigation, but also often return visit. Every morning, Huang Hanming decorate after work, will go to the hospital for treatment and intravenous drip, and then back to work, almost every night until 9 pm to go home from work, after home also summarized work.

Since the end of January, especially after the "city closure" in Wuhan, the pressure of prevention and control in Hubei Province has gradually increased. In the words of Jiang Chaoliang, the party chief of Hubei Province, "the weak point of epidemic prevention and control is in the countryside. For the countryside and the communities, controlling the returnees is the key. "

The task of prevention and control was then conveyed to Shuizhai village. Since the Spring Festival, Huang Hanming almost no rest, the village of the investigation by the personnel are recorded in his files. Especially for people returning home from Wuhan for the Spring Festival, Huang Hanming took them as the focus of prevention and control.

During the anti-epidemic period, the new Anlu pneumonia control and Prevention Headquarters issued more than a dozen circular orders, Huang Hanming took a large loudspeaker, shouting around the village, everywhere propaganda. He posted every order, even handed out leaflets, just to get it in place and let everyone know.

"He (Huang Hanming) volunteered to take on many days of duty. When I asked him why he didn't take a break, he said he didn't think about it, he wouldn't fuck anyone! " Huang said that throughout the Spring Festival holiday, it was difficult for the family to find his younger brother Huang Hanming for a meal, he has little spare time.

Killed in the line of duty

After a nine-day battle against the plague, Huang finally fell to his post.

On the evening of January 29, Huang Hanming was admitted to the Anlu Hospital of traditional Chinese medicine after suffering from bilateral emphysema caused by fatigue, according to the official wechat account "Shi Hua an Lu" of the Anlu municipal party committee's Propaganda Department. The next day, as soon as his condition improved, he hurried back to work.

On January 31, Huang Han finished infusion in the morning, returned to the village in the afternoon to continue to participate in duty, the same night after returning home, only to fall into shock, was rushed to the hospital. On February 1, Huang's condition suddenly deteriorated. At 10:00 on the same day, after the hospital tried to rescue invalid, Huang Hanming unfortunately died on duty.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
After the hospital all-out rescue invalid, Huang Hanming unfortunately died in the line of duty. Photo courtesy of the respondents

On February 1, Erken Jiang Tulahong, a member of the Standing Committee of the CPC Hubei Provincial Committee and head of the United Front Work Department, and his party went to the village of Shuizhai in Yandian town of Anlu city to pay their respects to the families of Comrade Huang Hanming, who was killed in the front line of Epidemic Prevention.

Erkengjiang Tolahong said that Secretary Huang is an excellent representative of our grass-roots cadres. He fell on the front line of Epidemic Prevention and put the safety of the people's lives above his own, this is the greatest positive energy in our epidemic prevention and interdiction campaign, and it is an example for us to follow. I hope you can turn your grief into strength and continue to do the job that Secretary Huang didn't finish.

The next day, the Anlu Municipal Party Committee announced that in the face of the sudden outbreak, Comrade Huang Hanming resolutely shoulder the territorial responsibility of preventing and controlling the spread of the epidemic. At the last moment of his life, he still in the village work group Shuizhai to explain the work.

"He is such a person, not for personal gain, the interests of the masses and the Party always in mind, in the first place, " Huang said of his younger brother, Huang Hanming.

Son Asks to fight "to carry on his father's legacy. "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Photo courtesy of the respondents

"I am Huang Lei. In order to carry on my father's legacy and complete the unfinished business of my father, Huang Hanming, I asked the organization to fight to fight against the front line of the epidemic. I am also a veteran of the armed police. I am of good physical quality and strong mind. Going to the front is like going to the battlefield... "

On February 5, a letter signed "Huang Lei" request to the hands of the village Party organization. On the same day, a group of Water Village Party members issued a message "need a party member to participate in volunteer patrol work" , Huang Lei decided to relay registration.

Huang said his younger brother, Huang Hanming, had a strict upbringing. He often taught his son to always remember that he came from a peasant family and to live and work well according to his ability. After Huang Hanming left, Huang Lei inherited his father's will, to the prevention and control of the first line on duty patrol.

"The death of his brother was a big blow to the family, " Huang said, especially since Huang's wife had been in poor health and the family had lost their "pillar of support. ".

The _ paper _ noted that recently, party members and cadres at all levels have successively died in the line of duty, falling on the front line of Epidemic Prevention and control, these include Datong Lingqiu County in Shanxi Province, Dajing community in Nanyang, Changling County in Jilin Province, Xuzhou Tongshan District in Jiangsu Province, Huainan in Anhui Province, Gaojia town in Tianfu new district, Meishan city, Sichuan Province, Datong District, Huainan in Hunan Province, etc. .

This issue is edited by Chang Chen
